histogram.summary:
Records whether a request was deferred due to a missing bound cookie. Recorded every time a request covered by a bound session completes either with a success or a failure.
"Covered by a bound session" means that a request will be deferred if it's missing a bound cookie.
{Type}

This histogram records how many times sync promos have been shown (including
the current one) across all access points when {Action} the {AccessPoint}
sync promo (Android Only).
